		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸牙兽进行突抓、右挠、左划三段攻击，分别造成<span color="#99ff87">30%x3,50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，圣骸牙兽卷成球朝玩家滚动，期间接触造成<span color="#99ff87">10%</span><span>伤害，滚动结束后挥扫一下，造成</span><span color="#99ff87">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="438" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每45s-60s，圣骸牙兽扫出一片绿色迷雾，隐蔽消失，顷刻突然出现在玩家上方并落地，造成<span color="#99ff87">80%</span><span>伤害，形成荆棘区，其会二次爆炸造成</span><span color="#99ff87">100%</span><span>伤害，并形成</span><span color="#00bd2c">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#00bd2c">噬骸能量块·草</span><span color="#00bd2c">」</span><span>；此时牙兽失去强化，6s后则会被牙兽吸收恢复强化。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="425">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_16.png')" x="720" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1392" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1391" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1391" y="713">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸牙兽进行右抓、左挠、尾翘三段攻击，分别造成<span color="#99ff87">60%,70%,90%</span><span>伤害，其中尾翘产生3道直线移动的棘藤，接触造成</span><span color="#99ff87">80%,40%,20%,8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="422" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，圣骸牙兽冲过来，用尖锐的尾部用力横扫，造成<span color="#99ff87">100%</span><span>伤害，同时产生一道草刃剑气，造成</span><span color="#99ff87">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="425" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸牙兽从开局、瘫痪恢复后或者吸收<span color="#00bd2c">「噬骸能量块·草」</span><span>之后，将进行抗性强化：</span><span color="#00ea52">草抗+60%，其他抗性+30%</span><span>，并且全身变亮；该效果持续到其施放</span><span color="#00bd2c">「虎下山」</span><span>技能后，或被携带有</span><span color="#00bd2c">「噬骸能量块·草」</span><span>的玩家命中后失效。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#24a451" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#24a451">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸牙兽.assets/Image_20.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
