		<RichText x="9" y="957" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">正常</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="1017" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">噬骸</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="444" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">噬骸能量块·草：1次<span color="#99ff87">草元素</span><span>攻击，或6次其他元素攻击可拾取，命中可瘫痪圣骸牙兽。其存在6s，超时则会被圣骸牙兽夺取。<br/>持有噬骸能量块·草时命中圣骸牙兽则会令其强制瘫痪10s，并移除抗性提升，同时扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15%</span><span>生命值；噬骸能量块携带时，会反噬全队：每秒损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2%</span><span>生命值，持续10s，穿盾不致死。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
